1953,"It was narrated that Ibn 'Umar said:“Ghailan bin Salamah became Muslim and he had ten wives. The Prophet said to him: 'Choose four of them.' ”",9,109,,,,,,عبداللہ بن عمر رضی اللہ عنہما کہتے ہیں کہ  غیلان بن سلمہ رضی اللہ عنہ نے اسلام قبول کیا اور ان کے نک,1953,
1954,"It was narrated from 'Uqbah bin 'Amir:that the Prophet said: “The conditions most deserving to be fulfilled are those by means of which the private parts become permissible for you.”",9,110,,,,,,"عقبہ بن عامر رضی اللہ عنہ کہتے ہیں کہ  نبی اکرم صلی اللہ علیہ وسلم نے فرمایا:  سب سے زیادہ پوری کی ج",1954,
1955,,9,111,,,,,,"عبداللہ بن عمرو بن العاص رضی اللہ عنہما کہتے ہیں کہ  رسول اللہ صلی اللہ علیہ وسلم نے فرمایا:  مہر یا",1955,
1956,"It was narrated from Abu Musa that the Messenger of Allah said:'Whoever has a slave woman and teaches her good manners and educates her, then sets her free and marries her, will have two rewards. Any man from among the People of the Book who believed in his Prophet and believed in Muhammad will have two rewards. Any slave who does his duty towards Allah and towards his masters will have two rewards.” (Sahih)(one of the narrators) Salih said: “Sha'bi said: 'I have given this (Hadith) to you for little effort on your part. A rider would travel to Al-Madinah for less than this.' ”",9,112,,,,,,"ابوموسیٰ اشعری رضی اللہ عنہ کہتے ہیں کہ  رسول اللہ صلی اللہ علیہ وسلم نے فرمایا:  جس کے پاس لونڈی ہو",1956,
1957,"It was narrated that Anas said:“Safiyyah was given to Dihyah Al-Kalbi (as his share of the war booty), then she was given to the Messenger of Allah after that. He married her, and made her ransom (i.e., freedom from slavery) her dowry.” (Sahih)Hammad said: “Abdul-'Aziz said to Thabit: 'O Abu Muhammad! Did you ask Anas what her bridal-money was?' He said: 'Her bridal-money was her freedom.' ”",9,113,,,,,,انس رضی اللہ عنہ کہتے ہیں کہ  پہلے ام المؤمنین صفیہ رضی اللہ عنہا دحیہ کلبی رضی اللہ عنہ کے حصہ میں ,1957,
1958,"It was narrated from 'Aishah:that the Messenger of Allah (ﷺ) set Safiyyah free, and made her ransom her dowry, and he married her",9,114,,,,,,ام المؤمنین عائشہ رضی اللہ عنہا سے روایت ہے کہ  رسول اللہ صلی اللہ علیہ وسلم نے ام المؤمنین صفیہ رضی,1958,
